<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.5.6">
<l>kiḻakkil kuṭimaṉṉar kēṭilā tārai</l>
<l>yaḻippāṉ niṉaintiṭṭav vāḻi yataṉāl</l>
<l>viḻikku maḷavilē vēraṟut tāṉaik</l>
<l>kuḻaṟkaṇiyā kakkuḻal vārāyak kākkāy</l>
<l rend="indent">kōvintaṉ ṟaṉkuḻal vārāyak kākkāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Caw! Caw! Comb the curly hair of he who,</l>
<l rend="indent">having decided to destroy the indestructible kings</l>
<l rend="indent">of the clans in the East,</l>
<l rend="indent">rooted them out in the blink of an eye with [his] discus</l>
<l>Caw! Caw! Comb the culry hair of Govinda.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
